49:50.530 --> 49:51.823
- Hey.
- How are you?

49:51.989 --> 49:53.074
Great.

49:54.117 --> 49:55.910
Josh, Kristen and Taylor.

49:56.077 --> 49:57.078
- Hey.
- How are you?

49:57.203 --> 49:58.287
