with her real husband.

51:23.247 --> 51:26.667
David, how much money
did you lose importing Cuban cigars?

51:26.834 --> 51:28.169
That guy looked very honest.

51:28.336 --> 51:30.129
He was in his bathing suit!

51:30.296 --> 51:34.509
