Hello?

52:38.698 --> 52:41.367
Phil! Buddy, how are you?

52:42.285 --> 52:43.786
Rob!

52:44.912 --> 52:46.205
Nelson!

52:47.415 --> 52:49.750
All right, don't worry, man. I understand.

52:50.459 --> 52:53.254
