54:07.203 --> 54:09.372
No. I deliver the meat.

54:09.705 --> 54:10.957
I don't murder it.

54:11.290 --> 54:14.210
I chauffeur it around.

54:14.460 --> 54:16.170
Leo Tolstoy says that,

54:16.337 --> 54:18.422
"if a man earnestly seeks
a righteous life,

54:18.589 --> 54:21.384
"his first act of abstinence
is from animal food."

54:22.635 --> 54:23.803
I did not know that.

54:23.928 --> 54:25.179
Sir Thomas More said,

54:25.221 --> 54:27.765
"The Utopians feel that
slaughtering our fellow creatures

54:27.932 --> 54:30.059
"gradually destroys
the sense of compassion

54:30.267 --> 54:33.437
"which is the finest sentiment
of which our human nature is capable."

54:36.273 --> 54:37.525
That's interesting.

54:41.904 --> 54:43.197
Can we keep this our secret?

54:44.991 --> 54:46.784
Can I stay here a few days?

54:47.952 --> 54:49.704
I need to get to know you.

54:50.913 --> 54:53.791
