Hey, should you be painting like this?

55:52.058 --> 55:53.392
Because I can do this.

55:53.559 --> 55:55.728
I can do the painting. I'm happy to do it.

55:58.773 --> 56:00.107
Thank you for being here.

56:00.775 --> 56:02.109
I'm glad I'm here.

56:02.151 --> 56:04.320
- But I'm excited to do the painting.
- Yeah?

56:04.445 --> 56:05.885
From now on, let me do the painting.

56:05.905 --> 56:07.114
- All right.
- Okay.

56:07.281 --> 56:08.949
I got you some French fries.

56:09.116 --> 56:11.452
- You got French fries, too?
- Yes.

56:11.619 --> 56:13.162
And there might be
something else in there.

56:13.287 --> 56:14.497
Really?

56:14.663 --> 56:16.248
A little treat?

56:17.500 --> 56:19.794
You got me two burgers!

56:20.795 --> 56:22.755
So, I'm trying to cancel
tomorrow night with Emma

56:22.922 --> 56:25.674
